<HEADLINE>
REPUBLICAN FOREIGN-POLICY PERSPECTIVES: MORALISTS VS. REALISTS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By NORMAN LEVINE  
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (RETRANSMITTING INHERITING-1, INHERITING-2 AND INHERITING-3 FOR
THOS
 &UR; E WHO MIGHT HAVE MISSED THIS SPECIAL PACKAGE
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-02-28-00 0104EST &QL; 
