   &UR; SCIENCE &AMP; TECHNOLOGY &LR;  &QC;  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; HOW THE WORLD MIGHT END &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By and large, scientists are an optimistic bunch. Some of them
can even remain cheerful when pondering something that most people
would regard as deeply depressing: the eventual destruction of the
earth. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Iowa, Michigan Editors) &QL;
