percent Barnesandnoble.com, and last year it launched bol.com in
Europe.
</P>
<P>
   Last December, Time Warner's Book of the Month Club and
Doubleday Direct's Literary Guild announced that they were joining
forces on the Internet.
</P>
<P>
   But beyond all the panic and the consolidation, bits of the
book-club business are finding their way on to the Internet.
</P>
<P>
   Doubleday Direct has employed Seth Radwell, an e-commerce man
who helped launch Bertelsmann's online retailing, to run Doubleday
