gets the team he couldn't have for the first-round matches against
Zimbabwe: Andre Agassi and Pete Sampras (who missed the earlier one
with an injury). Now the question is what to do with Zimbabwe hero
Chris Woodruff.
</P>
<P>
   AMERICAS-CUP (Auckland, New Zealand) _ Trying to overcome light
winds that have made this a stop-and-start America's Cup final, the
New Zealanders, with a 3-0 lead, try to wrap up the Cup in Race 4.
By Herb McCormick.
</P>
