<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-28 15:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0967 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l BC-MEDICATED-FIRST-LADIE     02-28 1572
</HEADER>
<BODY>
