   Outrage and disbelief throughout the land.
</P>
<P>
   41 shots explain if you can.
</P>
<P>
   48 hours to contemplate.
</P>
<P>
   48 to get their story straight.
</P>
<P>
   48 hours well isn't it great?
</P>
<P>
   If you are the law you get 48.
