   &UR; NONSUBSCRIBERS: To publish any of these ``separate-buy'' feature
articles, they must be purchased. Please contact one of these sales
representatives: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   --U.S. and Canada: DEBRA WEYDERT in New Jersey at
1-732-390-4480; fax, 732-390-4697.
</P>
<P>
   --Europe and Asia: KARL HORWITZ in Paris at 47-42-17-11; fax,
47-42-80-44 or 47-42-18-81; telex, 282-942.
</P>
<P>
   --Latin America: ANA PENA in New York, 310-798-0970; fax,
310-798-7338. &QL;
</P>
