expected to announce a penalty for Darryl Strawberry late Monday
for his failing of a drug test last month. By Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
   AMERICAS-CUP (Auckland, New Zealand) _ Trying to overcome light
winds that have made this a stop-and-start America's Cup final, the
New Zealanders, with a 3-0 lead, try to wrap up the Cup tonight in
Race 4. By Herb McCormick.
</P>
