sleep, without exercising or dieting, claim local on-air
personalities who say they've been losing weight using the product
in recent months. But not everyone is convinced that the
weight-loss supplement is such a good idea, and some go so far as
to say it's just a ridiculous scam. By CAROLYN POIROT. Story has
moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
